      <title>特朗普胜选后，里昂证券策略师看好印度股市而非中国股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/clsa-strategists-favor-india-equities-over-china-after-trump-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里昂证券 (CLSA) 策略师改变了对中国股票的战术性增持策略，并增持了印度股票，理由是美国总统当选人唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 上任后，贸易紧张局势可能再度加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/clsa-strategists-favor-india-equities-over-china-after-trump-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 14:28:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国工业生产因罢工和飓风影响而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/us-industrial-production-falls-on-strike-hurricane-disruptions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受波音公司机械师罢工和两次飓风的影响，美国十月份工业生产连续第二个月下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/us-industrial-production-falls-on-strike-hurricane-disruptions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 14:17:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
