    <item>
      <title>德鲁肯米勒领导的家族办公室加大对美国银行股的投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/druckenmiller-leads-family-offices-boosting-us-bank-stock-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个季度，斯坦利·德鲁肯米勒 (Stanley Druckenmiller) 的家族理财室带领全球富豪投资公司增加了对美国银行股的配置，使他们能够从金融股上涨中获利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/druckenmiller-leads-family-offices-boosting-us-bank-stock-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 13:49:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟动用天然气储备，德国警告天然气补充风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/germany-warns-of-gas-refill-risk-as-eu-taps-deeper-into-reserves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲的天然气储备消耗速度比预期的要快，而且随着夏季燃料价格上涨，最大天然气消费国德国警告称，下一个供暖季节存在补充风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/germany-warns-of-gas-refill-risk-as-eu-taps-deeper-into-reserves</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 13:04:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员认为美联储 12 月降息的可能性仅为 50%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/treasuries-trim-weekly-loss-with-focus-on-data-and-fed-speakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们认为，下个月降息就像掷硬币一样，因为强劲的经济数据使美联储官员有能力采取更为谨慎的宽松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/treasuries-trim-weekly-loss-with-focus-on-data-and-fed-speakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 11:05:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市下跌，因交易员削减降息押注；赛诺菲股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/european-stocks-fall-as-traders-trim-rate-cut-bets-sanofi-drops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔发表谨慎言论后，交易员降低了对美联储 12 月降息的预期，欧洲股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/european-stocks-fall-as-traders-trim-rate-cut-bets-sanofi-drops</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 08:23:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受供应过剩担忧和美元走低影响，油价本周下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国经济和消费数据好坏参半、美元走强的持续影响以及对明年市场将陷入供应过剩的担忧，油价下跌，进一步加剧了本周的跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 23:33:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
